WEBVTT

00:11:29.406 --> 00:11:33.985
To backtrack, the kind of
intuitive position of basketball

00:11:34.009 --> 00:11:38.061
is it's the sport
where talent matters most

00:11:38.085 --> 00:11:41.688
and coaching and organizational
fit matter least.

00:11:41.712 --> 00:11:45.609
If you put LeBron on a team of all Sirans,

00:11:45.633 --> 00:11:48.189
you can basically guarantee
you'll make the play-offs

00:11:48.213 --> 00:11:51.364
and he actually has made the finals
several times with teams of --

00:11:51.388 --> 00:11:54.676
so it's like, it doesn't really matter
who's with LeBron,

00:11:54.700 --> 00:11:58.450
you can put a bunch of stiffs
and it's fine, right?

00:11:59.188 --> 00:12:02.974
In fact, the two greatest
basketball teams of all time,